node.text:
This trip to Waco was something I’ll never forget!! Staying in the Hillcrest Estate that Chip & Joanna Gaines renovated, chatting and laughing with good friends till 2am every night, and lots of shopping!! What more could I ask for?!
.
Here’s a little recap of my trip. Can’t wait to go back to Waco again!!
.
.
.
.

node.text:
Spring cleaning is in full effect over here and the first thing I did was “strip”my white discolored bedding. I have heard about laundry stripping but I was honestly was a bit skeptical so I had to give it a try for myself!!
.
The results completely shocked me and now nothing in our home is safe from “laundry stripping”. It’s my new obsession!!
.
Click here for direct links to everything I used to make my white sheets new again! 
http://liketk.it/3cj3E
.
.
.

node.text:
Finishing our basement has been so fun and watching each space come together is so rewarding!! This room is a mini suite with an attached bathroom. I love how it turned out! The warm neutral and earthy tones and textures give it a welcoming vibe! Best decisions made was to install wall to wall 100% waterproof vinyl flooring from @officialselectsurfaces it’s gorgeous and locks together perfectly!
.
Check out my video and see this room come to life in under 2 mins!
.
#roomrenovation #building #woodworking #diyprojects #bedroomvibes #homedecor #interiordesign #interiordesigner #cozyvibes #bedroomdesign

We wanted to add a modern style pergola to our newly refinished deck and the @tojagrid system was the perfect fit! We put up the 4x4 double pergola kit.
.
It took us about 2 days to build and completely transformed the look and feel of the whole space. I love the clean lines of this pergola and couldn’t be happier with how it turned out!
.
#pergola #tojagrid #backyard #backyarddesign #diy #diyproject #woodworking #outdoorliving #outdoordining #pergoladesign

node.text:
This project has been years in the making and now that it’s done I can’t believe this is my living room!! I have been wanting beams for so long, seriously they made the biggest impact to our living room and I couldn’t be more excited with how it turned out!
.
These beams by @ornamentalmoulding made this weekend project super easy, now if you need me I’ll be lying on the floor just staring at these beauties!! 😍
.
.
.
.

node.text:
Remember when I switched up my dining spaces?? Well that also included my outdoor dining space!! I have have 2 tables that are indoor/outdoor tables, and I decided to swap them and I love it!! 
.
Do you like eating outside during the warmer months? It’s one of our favorites ways to enjoy our backyard!!
.
.
.
.

.

.

Open to US residence only, winner will be announced in my stories and on this post!! Good luck!!
.
.
.
.

node.text:
My bathroom got a new rug and it seriously feels like it was made for this space! The colors, design, and style are exactly what I have been looking for!!
.
You can use my code: GREYBIRCH for a discount on a @ruggable rug of your very own!! These rugs are super functional for a bathroom too because…are you ready…..they’re machine washable!!! #micdrop 🎤
.
Also did you know they now have cushion rug pads?!? Ya they are amazing, non-slip, and so comfortable on your feet! 🙌🏻
#ruggablepartner
.
.
.
.
